title: Does my phone support flash playback? If not, can I install a third-party flash player for flash playback?
answer:
Your phone is not preinstalled with any flash players. 

 [The downloaded third-party flash players cannot be used for flash playback, because Adobe did not release any plug-ins for Android 4.2 and old plug-ins are not available on the Android 4.2 operating system.]()
